page.title: 05Ecology fauna Chaldon Hills
page.content: The following species were observed:- {Animals Badger,Deer (Roe and Sika),Fox,Hare, Rabbit,Stoat,Weasel. {Birds} Blackbird,Black headed gull,Blue tit,Buzzard,Chaffinch,Crow,Dunnock, English partridge,Great tit,Herring gull, Jay, Magpie,Meadow pipit, Pheasant,Pigeon, Red-legged partridge, Sparrow hawk, Starling,Swallow, Whitethroat, Yellowhammer. {Butterflies Brimstone,Common blue,Gatekeeper,Large white,Marbled white,Meadow brown, Painted lady,Red admiral,Small copper, Small white.
